<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Geospatial Analytics for Revenue Growth</h1>
    <p class="subhead">Twelve proven spatial analysis techniques that drive sales performance and territory clarity.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Territory Optimization</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Optimize territory boundaries by workload, potential, and geography.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Increase efficiency and coverage; balance rep workloads.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Balance territories to maximize rep productivity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Market Penetration Analysis</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Measure customer density vs. population to find underserved markets.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Identify high-potential, low-penetration growth zones.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Locate zip codes with high opportunity but low sales.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Customer Clustering</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Group customers by geography and attributes for campaigns.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Target localized promotions and discover neighborhood patterns.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Identify clusters of similar buyers for localized outreach.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Site Selection</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Evaluate new site locations using demographics and competition.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Minimize expansion risk; rank potential cities or regions.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Score and select the best area for a new flagship location.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Competitive Intelligence</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Map competitor locations and market share distribution.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Spot competitor strongholds; uncover whitespace opportunities.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Map competitor dominance and identify open market areas.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Catchment Area Analysis</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Define drive-time and service zones to optimize coverage.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Improve service reach and ensure area balance.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Define 15-minute drive zones for each branch.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Sales Performance Mapping</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Visualize revenue, quota attainment, and trends geographically.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Quickly spot high/low performance zones.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Create a heatmap of sales revenue per territory.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Proximity Analysis</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Measure distance to customers and prospects for routing.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Prioritize nearby accounts; improve conversion rates.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Find all prospects within 5 miles of top clients.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Demographic Profiling</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Overlay demographic data on sales territories for targeting.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Match products to income or lifestyle segments.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Align marketing spend with high-income neighborhoods.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Expansion Opportunity Scoring</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Rank regions by growth potential using composite metrics.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Focus investment where ROI potential is highest.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Score metro areas for expansion readiness.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Route Optimization</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Calculate efficient travel routes for field reps.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Reduce travel costs; increase visit frequency.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Optimize daily call routes by geography.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 class="title">Spatial Correlation Analysis</h3>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Detect relationships between sales and location-based factors.</p>
      <p><strong>Value:</strong> Predict outcomes and identify key geographic drivers.</p>
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Correlate store sales with foot-traffic intensity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

